    "16619615184d0ec658": {
      "type": "nine15--ctas",
      "settings": {
        "title": "ART OF THE UNMATCHED™",
        "text": "<p><b>Words by Conni Reed</b></p>\n\n<p>The “Art of the Unmatched” is our trademarked design philosophy, and it’s the basis, foundation, and inspiration for our collection each season. The word unmatched is intentional – different than mismatched, unmatched is purposeful, varied, and unexpected, similar to each of our personal histories and lives. The Art of the Unmatched™ is representative of journey; a collage of sights,\nsounds, emotions and travels.</p>\n\n<p>We use vivid colors and unexpected textures each season as these things have a physiological effect on us. There are many studies around the impact that color has on our state of mind and happiness. The color and textural juxtapositions get our endorphins flowing. This is why people describe the bags as ‘joyful’, and that is foundational to the Art of the Unmatched™.</p>",
        "link_text": "",
        "link_url": "",
        "button_text": "",
        "button_url": "",
        "btn_style": "primary",
        "text_color": "#000000",
        "gradient": "",
        "per_row": 0,
        "align_boxes_left": false,
        "large_images": false,
        "inline_ctas": false,
        "match_row": false,
