    "16619638557b4ceb53": {
      "type": "nine15--ctas",
      "settings": {
        "title": "DESIGN PHILOSOPHY",
        "text": "<p><b>Manifesting Through Art</b></p>\n\n<p>As a result of my personal journey, I developed a heightened level of empathetic awareness to people, and especially, to their unseen journey. For that reason, I became interested in the art of collage—telling a story through bits and pieces of vintage scraps and modern images. I then began collaging on a different medium, handbags. In the same way, the colors, patterns, and texture tell an emotional story— an unexpected story, just like people often do.</p>\n\n<p>It is created from a place of love, from a place meant to elevate and pull out the joy that people feel and want to remember — translating who they are on the inside, even if their outside or current circumstance doesn’t match.</p>\n\n<p>This is why we make lots of unique combinations of the same silhouette each season. The Classic Tote is the best-selling silhouette today, 16 years after we started making it. Each season, we make anywhere from 12 to 20 new combinations of this bag because we celebrate the unique stories of people in honor of their journey.</p>",
        "link_text": "",
        "link_url": "",
