    "1661963956baf3619b": {
      "type": "nine15--ctas",
      "settings": {
        "title": "THE JOURNEY IS REAL",
        "text": "<p><b>A Resilient Community</b></p>\n\n<p>The Art of the Unmatched™ has opened doors to meeting amazing people motivated to bring joy through their work. We set out to find and form mutually beneficial relationships and friendships. We are committed to the work and to the people we work with.</p>\n\n<p>We each come from different backgrounds and bring unique contributions. A common thread of resiliency, care and shared values brings us together. With gratitude and hope we move forward, excitedly anticipating future possibilities.</p>",
